# Cloud Synchronization Setup (Supabase)
# ==================================
# 1. Create a free account at https://supabase.com
# 2. Create a new project.
# 3. Go to SQL Editor and run the script inside `supabase_schema.sql` to create your tables.
# 4. Go to Project Settings -> API and copy your URL and anon key here.
# 5. Rename this file from `.env.example` to `.env`

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your-supabase-project-url.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key-here
